collections.name: Digital Bodyscape 76-3 etnah
collections.description: Lee Kun-Yong is one of the most influential figures in the Korean avant-garde movement and continues his provocative practice in diverse media such as performance, video, sculpture, and installation. His work attends to the physical body as a medium where the self meets the world.Digital Bodyscape 76-3 is the first expansion of the Bodyscape series to the digital world, which Lee Kun-Yong has been working on for decades. It is also an Interactive NFT presenting the moment in which the artist''s body extends to the digital world. The performance conducted by the avatar of the artist will be created with the colors of the canvas and the paint selected by the NFT holder on the platform exclusively accessed by the holders. The holders mint a personalized NFT through the performance conducted by the avatar. Every single one of the 1,976 NFTs becomes the one and only artwork.

collections.name: Delitown
collections.description:
Delitown is the first platform that connects the virtual and real world.

You can own or rent land and buildings in Delitown. If you become the owner of the building, you can directly move in a number of amenities, including a restaurant.
The Delitown team will continue to provide real world delivery restaurants, etc. in Delitown. Users who use Delitown can talk to each other, play games together, and enjoy various amenities. In real world, if you're hungry, you can order from within virtual world. The restaurant in Delitown, where the order was received, will be directly connected to the real restaurant and delivery will be made.
Through Delitown, anyone can run a restaurant and earn money. We invite you to Delitown, a virtual world connected to the real world.

GAEGUNEEZ NFTs are based on eco-friendly characters GAEGUNEEZ, with the goal of changing the perception that protecting the environment is difficult and bothersome, especially targeting the metaverse generation.

GAEGUNEEZ will build an ecosystem where environmentalism, an important value to our times, can prosper in metaverse and provide socially meaningful experiences.

collections.name: Meta Toy Squad

Born in agreement with The Iron Squad, a popular variety show aired on Korean broadcasting company Channel A, MTS offers fans of the show time to interact with the cast and crew, as well as other benefits. Holders will also receive item ticket NFTs for the upcoming P2E game, MTDZ The Game. The item ticket NFT will no longer be minted, and the MTS will be revealed in June 2022.

Klaybank is a protocol that provides various cryptocurrency Lending&Borrowing services in the Klaytn network. Any user of Klaytn Network can deposit his or her KCT (Klaytn Compatible Token) assets to Klaybank to receive interest and KBTs (KlayBankToken) in return.
On the other hand, while users who wish to loan must provide their KCT assets as collateral to loan other KCT assets and pay interest, they too can receive KBTs as they have added value to the community.

collections.name: ArcheWorld_Land
collections.description: This is the official Land NFT of ArcheWorld. This verifies that the Land NFT owner can permanently own the land designated on seamless open-world of ArcheWorld. Owners can participate in production activities directly by installing buildings in the game, or they can lease their land to others and collect rent with Blue Salt(BSLT) every month. Owners may generate earnings by converting Blue Salt(BSLT) to BORA.

collections.description:
World's first decentralized music copyright investment NFT Project 
Chris Brown and Mintpang started the first Decentralized Music Copyright Investment NFT project.
This project publishes a total of 10,000 Klaytn-based NFTs for Chris Brown's new songs, NFT holders(owners) can receive monthly music revenue distribution through staking.

If NFT owners support and promote artists, the rewards will increase accordingly. Together with the artists you support, you can make a companion community.

Meta Toy Gamers (MTG) by SBXG (Sandbox Gaming) is a collection of 5,999 PFP NFTs designed as members of Meta Toy world ecosystem and a spin-off collection of Meta Toy DragonZ (MTDZ). SBXG aims to establish one of the most powerful gamer communities and esports brand in blockchain game realm.
MTG holders will be granted with various online and offline benefits related to games and esports. Core milestones such as DAO team governance and P2E game guilds are to be unfolded through further roadmap activation.
Join Meta Toy Gamers. Slay your games

collections.name: SYLTARE, Dawn of East
collections.description:
"If one can imagine it, it exists."
Who would win in a battle? General Lee Sun-Shin or Alexander the Great? Would Robin Hood be able to best an elf with a bow? What if Haetae were to battle Pikachu? Let your imagination run wild in SYLTARE.

SYLTARE is a trading card game using NFTs. In the world of SYLTARE, various heroes of legends and history are yours to own and use in strategic battles.

How did all these heroes come to exist in a single space and time? What is happening in the universe? Secrets will unfold as you fight your way through many battles alongside your favorite heroes. It should also never be forgotten that a just reward rightfully belongs to the victors.

collections.name: Raving Goblins
collections.description:
Raving Goblins come from Musica, a small planet hidden few light years away. Their seemingly chaotic world runs on a cosmic energy fueled by music, dance and art. In order to create the energy they are bound to party 24/7, making them the biggest party lovers in the known and unknown galaxies.

Raving Goblins are the coolest and sickest intergalactic dancers always looking to rave. Now, they are bringing their rave to Earth.

Are you ready to party? Only 10,456 unique Raving Goblins will participate in the first rave.
